title: 6 Creative Recipes Using 1 Can of Sardines ! (Part 1)
description:
Part 2 (soon) https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9AgT9zqCmeM Canned sardines are so underrated ! Those preserved fish are a essential to every smart chef’s pantry. French Marinated Sardines in Escabeche sauce. Japanese Unagi Don with Canned Sardines. Italian Pasta with Sardines and Fennel : Pasta con le sarde. Those cans are GENIUS !

In this videos I am wearing my Pizza T-shirt ! Buy it and support the french guy’s adventures here :
